info:
Students develop the advanced pediatric health assessment knowledge and skills needed for the pediatric nurse practitioner/pediatric clinical nurse specialist. Selected nursing interventions and integrative therapies are examined for their application to the pediatric population.  

Prerequisites: 
NURS 5200 Holistic Health Assessment & Therapeutics for APNs;
NURS 5222 Advanced Physiology;
NURS 5229 Clinical Pharmacotherapeutics 
or Instructor Consent
